FOR ALVIN AILEY?
I HAD LOTS OF BUTTERFLIES THEN.

10:44.330 --> 10:45.183
- REMEMBER, SHE TOOK
ALL THOSE DEEP BREATHS,

10:45.230 --> 10:47.676
AND WAS, LIKE,
SHAKING HER MUSCLES OUT,

10:47.710 --> 10:48.677
LIKE...
[panï¬ng]

